[h1]Changelog[/h1]

[h2]v0.1.0 — 2026-03-17[/h2]
[b]Initial release[/b]

[list]
[*] Proximity Autopsy Table — right-click near ZVV autopsy tables and corpses for table-quality autopsies
[*] RV Bridge Remote Autopsy — use a morgue table inside your RV from outside the vehicle
[*] Morgue Table Caching — table locations persist after visiting the RV interior
[*] Table Status Indicator — colour-coded tooltip (Ready / Occupied / Needs Cleaning)
[*] 5 sandbox options for fine-tuning detection ranges and toggling features
[/list]
